    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The exterior has noticeable rust, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling extensively. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tears, and several interior components are missing or broken. It currently has difficulty starting and runs roughly, suggesting it may need major engine or transmission work soon. This would be best suited as a project car or for someone looking for a parts vehicle.",
